metadata.description:
Decided to make a remix of an all-time K-Pop favorite of Taeyang's Wedding Dress! The song and his vocals are just beautiful and I really wanted to give that uplifting sound that resonates the heartfelt emotions from the lyrics!

**If anyone could send me the English acapella, so I can make the English version, that would be awesome!**

DOWNLOAD HERE:
http://bit.ly/1vEwK3P
